name: Can you take a picture of us?
description:
Since I was in my B&W file this morning, I pulled out my best photo from when I went in Salatiga, Indonesia.
I was already walking way back home with my friends and looked in front of me, i found 2 adults and 1 child looking at me from a far, maybe i think they know im doing street photograph for my job because i wearing a film camera strap around my neck. And when i already in front of them walking and said "excuse me sir" they screaming at me "SIS, CAN YOU TAKE A PICTURE OF US?????" 
i said "ok! wait!" 
i took out my camera strap from my neck and had my lens pop out to take this picture, i said "of course lemme take the picture of you, stay still 1.. 2.. 3.. smile!" and that's the result. And when i went back to their area i only found 1 of them doing their job as scavengers and give him the group photo print.
This photo give me such mixed feelings. 

using ilford delta 400
